      </div>
      
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Emergency Call Optimization</h3>
          <p>Specialized optimization for urgent service searches like "emergency plumber" and "24/7 HVAC repair" to capture high-value emergency calls when customers need help most.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-map-marked-alt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Hyper-Local Service Area SEO</h3>
          <p>Target specific neighborhoods, cities, and service areas with location-based content that establishes your presence in every community you serve.</p>
        </div>
        
