          <p>Strategic content and SEO campaigns aligned with seasonal demand - HVAC maintenance seasons, landscaping growing seasons, and roofing storm response periods.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Trust & Credibility Building</h3>
